📊 VAE vs Autoencoder

| Feature      | Autoencoder    | VAE             |
| ------------ | -------------- | --------------- |
| Output       | Reconstruction | Generation      |
| Latent space | Fixed          | Probabilistic   |
| Use case     | Compression    | Data generation |

