🚀 Applications

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Autoencoders

* Image compression
* Noise removal
* Feature extraction

---

VAE

* Image generation
* Data augmentation
* Anomaly detection

---

⚠️ Challenges

❌ Blurry output in VAE
❌ Complex training
❌ Sensitive to hyperparameters

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🧠 Best Practices

✔ Normalize input data
✔ Use proper latent size
✔ Tune loss balance
✔ Use dropout

---

📊 Workflow

```text id="ae_flow"
Input Data
   ↓
Encoder
   ↓
Latent Space
   ↓
Decoder
   ↓
Reconstructed Output
```

